{"tid":456831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未能達成有效裁決　曾蔭權案陪審團再次解散","createTime":"2017-11-03T09:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T03:59:41.000Z","uid":136994,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9486b8af57e494223b06b5a02adf258625058579","tid":456831,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171103/s00001/1509691743755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171103%2Fs00001%2F1509691743755&d=xfNzcqQ1qKezir9uKNQTEy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=2e17b344\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171103%2Fs00001%2F1509691743755&h=246a812e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171103/s00001/1509691743755</a><br />\n<br />\n前特首曾蔭權被控行政長官收受利益罪，4男4女組成的陪審團，由昨日下午退庭商議至今，最終未能達到最少6比2的比數作出有效裁決。法官陳慶偉指，明白陪審團未能達至大比數有效裁決，正式宣布解散陪審團。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，曾蔭權涉嫌於2010年1月1日至2012年6月30日，無合法權限或合理辯解而接受利益、即深圳東海花園的三聯式住宅物業的整修及裝修工程，作為他作出或不作出憑其行政長官及行政會議主席身分而作的作為，即考慮及決定雄濤廣播有限公司（其後改名為香港數碼廣播有限公司，即DBC）提交的3項申請的報酬。"},{"pid":"a2a97b227ba43e260f788237f6fc53a7e46ae8c7","tid":456831,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2263f5b7e79954530e47eca6319733add9828121","tid":456831,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"有排審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b2315485cd15f5d9531d9c77acdc6bb2abe4a2","tid":456831,"uid":59976,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:21:29.000Z","msg":"無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">個人簽名<br 